                    <Footer/>
                    <WebAddress>https://www.cftc.gov/MarketReports/CottonOnCall/index.htm</WebAddress>
                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Cotton Futures</Header>
                <Paragraph>The "Cotton On-Call Report" shows the quantity of bought or sold call cotton on which the price has not been fixed, together with the respective futures on which the purchase or sale is based. Call cotton refers to physical cotton bought or sold, or contracted for purchase or sale at a price to be fixed later based upon a specified delivery month future’s price.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
