                <Header>Whistleblower Program</Header>
                <Paragraph>The Commission gives monetary incentives to whistleblowers who report possible Commodity Exchange Act violations that lead to a successful enforcement action. The Commission also provides antiretaliation protections, confidentiality, and privacy.</Paragraph>
